videos.headline: Van Buren punches in TD for Boise State
videos.description: Andrew Van Buren converts at the goal line to extend Boise State's lead over Fresno State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Van Buren punches in TD for Boise State) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shakir wins jump ball in end zone for Boise State TD
videos.description: Hank Bachmeier lofts a pass to Khalil Shakir, who beats his defender to score a touchdown for Boise State.
